===Noun===
{{wikipediapar|bryophyte}}
'''bryophyte'''
#{{botany}} any [[plant]] in which the [[gametophyte]] ([[haploid]]) stage of the lifecycle is the larger, persistent stage, and the [[sporophyte]] ([[diploid]]) stage is small and dependent upon the gametophyte.  Bryophytes include [[moss]]es, [[liverwort]]s, and [[hornwort]]s.

